  <body>
    <!-- wrapper starts -->
    <div class="wrapper">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="head_section">
          <div class="logo">
            <a href="#">
            <figure>
              <img alt="logo" height="31" src="https://gc-public-prod.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/assets/logo.png" width="71">
            </figure></a>
            <h1>EVIDENCE OF PERSONAL PROPERTY INSURANCE</h1>
          </div>
          <div class="date_sec last_br_btm">
            <h4>DATE(DD/MM/YYYY)</h4>
            <h3><%= Time.current.strftime("%m/%d/%Y") %></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clearfix"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="evid_main_blk">
          <div class="para_1">
            <p>THIS EVIDENCE OF PROPERTY INSURANCE IS ISSUED AS A MATTER OF INFORMATION ONLY AND CONFERS NO RIGHTS UPON THE ADDITIONAL INTEREST NAMED BELOW. THIS EVIDENCE DOES NOT AFFIRMATIVELY OR NEGATIVELY AMEND, EXTEND OR ALTER THE COVERAGE AFFORDED BY THE POLICIES BELOW. THIS EVIDENCE OF INSURANCE DOES NOT CONSTITUTE A CONTRACT BETWEEN THE ISSUING INSURER(S), AUTHORIZED REPRESENTATIVE OR PRODUCER, AND THE ADDITIONAL INTEREST.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="agency_main flt_lt">
            <div class="agency_left flt_lt">
              <h4>AGENCY</h4>
              <h2><%= @agency.contact_info["legal_name"] %></h2>
              <address>
                <%= @address.combined_street_address %> <%= @address.street_two %><br>
                <%= @address.city %>, <%= @address.state %>, <%= @address.zip_code %>
              </address>
            </div>
            <div class="agency_right flt_lt">
              <h4>PHONE(<span>A/C, No, Ext</span>):</h4>
              <h2><%= @agency.contact_info["phone"] %></h2>
            </div>
            <div class="clearfix"></div>
            <div class="fax_in">
              <h4>FAX (A/C No Ext):<span><%= @agency.contact_info["fax"] %></span></h4>
              <h4>EMAIL ADDRESS:<span><%= @agency.contact_info["email"] %></span></h4>
            </div>
            <div class="code_in clearfix">
              <div class="code flt_lt">
                <h4>CODE:</h4>
                <h2><%= @carrier_agency.external_carrier_id %></h2>
              </div>
              <div class="sub_code flt_lt">
                <h4>SUBCODE:</h4>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="cust_id">
              <h4>AGENCY CUSTOMER ID #:<span><%= @policy.primary_user.qbe_id %></span></h4>
            </div>
            <div class="insured_in">
              <h4>INSURED</h4>
              <h2><%= @policy.primary_user.profile.full_name %></h2>
              <address>
                <%= @policy.primary_insurable.primary_address.combined_street_address %> Apt. <br>
                <%= @policy.primary_insurable.primary_address.city %>, <%= @policy.primary_insurable.primary_address.state %>, <%= @policy.primary_insurable.primary_address.combined_zip_code() %>
              </address>
              <% unless @policy.users.nil? || @policy.users.count == 1 %>
              <h2>
                Additional Insured: 
                <% @policy.users.each_with_index do |u, index| %>
                  <% unless u.id == @policy.primary_user.id %>
                     <%= u.profile.full_name %><%= ", " unless index == (@policy.users.count - 2) %>
                  <% end %>
                <% end %>
              </h2>
              <% end %>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="company_main flt_lt">
            <div class="comp_in">
              <h4>COMPANY</h4>
              <address>
                Praetorian Insurance Company<br>
                One General Drive<br>
                Sun Prairie, WI 53596
              </address>
            </div>
            <div class="loan_in clearfix">
              <div class="loan_left flt_lt">
                <h4>LOAN NUMBER</h4>
              </div>
              <div class="loan_right flt_lt">
                <h4>POLICY NUMBER</h4><span><%= @policy.number %></span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="effect_in clearfix">
              <div class="eff_date flt_lt">
                <h4>EFFECTIVE DATE</h4><span><%= @policy.effective_date.strftime("%m/%d/%Y") %></span>
              </div>
              <div class="exp_date flt_lt">
                <h4>EXPIRATION DATE</h4><span><%= @policy.expiration_date.strftime("%m/%d/%Y") %></span>
              </div>
              <div class="cross flt_lt">
                <h2><%= @policy.auto_renew == true ? "X" : raw("&nbsp;") %></h2>
              </div>
              <div class="conti_in flt_lt">
                <h4>CONTINUED UNTIL<br>
                TERMINATED IF CHECKED</h4>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="prior">
              <h4>THIS REPLACES PRIOR EVIDENCE DATED:</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="empty">
              &nbsp;
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="clearfix"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="prop_head">
          <h2>PROPERTY INFORMATION</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="property_main_blk">
          <div class="prop_loca">
            <h4>LOCATION/DESCRIPTION</h4>
            <address>
              <%= @policy.primary_insurable.primary_address.combined_street_address %> Apt. <br>
              <%= @policy.primary_insurable.primary_address.city %>, <%= @policy.primary_insurable.primary_address.state %>, <%= @policy.primary_insurable.primary_address.combined_zip_code() %>
            </address>
          </div>
          <div class="prop_cont">
            <h2>THE POLICIES OF INSURANCE LISTED BELOW HAVE BEEN ISSUED TO THE INSURED NAMED ABOVE FOR THE POLICY PERIOD INDICATED. NOTWITHSTANDING ANY REQUIREMENT, TERM OR CONDITION OF ANY CONTRACT OR OTHER DOCUMENT WITH RESPECT TO WHICH THIS EVIDENCE OF PROPERTY INSURANCE MAY BE ISSUED OR MAY PERTAIN, THE INSURANCE AFFORDED BY THE POLICIES DESCRIBED HEREIN IS SUBJECT TO ALL THE TERMS, EXCLUSIONS AND CONDITIONS OF SUCH POLICIES. LIMITS SHOWN MAY HAVE BEEN REDUCED BY PAID CLAIMS.</h2>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="coverage_head">
          <h2>COVERAGEINFORMATION</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="coverage_main_blk clearfix">
          <div class="coverage_in flt_lt"><% covs_by_des = @policy.coverages.group_by{|cov| cov.designation }.transform_values{|vs| vs.first }; other_coverages = @policy.coverages.select{|cov| !['coverage_c', 'wind_hail', 'coverage_d', 'liability', 'medical'].include?(cov.designation) } %>
            <h4>COVERAGE/PERIL/FORMS</h4>
            <h2>&nbsp;</h2>
            <h2>C - Personal Property</h2>
            <h2>Wind/Hail Deductible</h2>
            <h2>D - Loss of Use</h2>
            <h2>E - Personal Liability (Limit)</h2>
            <h2 <% if other_coverages.blank? %>class="last_br_btm"<% end %>>F - Medical Payments (Limit)</h2>
            <% other_coverages.each.with_index do |cov, index| %>
            <h2 <% if index == other_coverages.length - 1 %>class="last_br_btm"<% end %>><%= cov.title %></h2>
            <% end %>
          </div>
          <div class="amount_in flt_lt">
            <h4>AMOUNT OF INSURANCE</h4>
            <h2>&nbsp;</h2>
            <h2><%= ActionController::Base.helpers.number_to_currency((covs_by_des['coverage_c']&.limit&.to_f || 0) / 100) %></h2>
            <h2>&nbsp;</h2>
            <h2><%= ActionController::Base.helpers.number_to_currency((covs_by_des['coverage_d']&.limit&.to_f || 0) / 100) %></h2>
            <h2><%= ActionController::Base.helpers.number_to_currency((covs_by_des['liability']&.limit&.to_f || 0) / 100) %></h2>
            <h2 <% if other_coverages.blank? %>class="last_br_btm"<% end %>><%= ActionController::Base.helpers.number_to_currency((covs_by_des['medical']&.limit&.to_f || 0) / 100) %></h2>
            <% other_coverages.each.with_index do |cov, index| %>
            <h2 <% if index == other_coverages.length - 1 %>class="last_br_btm"<% end %>><%= cov.limit ? ActionController::Base.helpers.number_to_currency(cov.limit.to_f / 100) : cov.deductible ? raw("&nbsp;") : "Included" %></h2>
            <% end %>           
          </div>
          <div class="deduct_in flt_lt">
            <h4>DEDUCTIBLE</h4>
            <h2 class="last_br_rt">&nbsp;</h2>
            <h2 class="last_br_rt"><%= ActionController::Base.helpers.number_to_currency(@policy.coverages.find_by(designation: "coverage_c").deductible.to_f / 100) %></h2>
            <h2 class="last_br_rt"><%= ActionController::Base.helpers.number_to_currency((covs_by_des['wind_hail']&.deductible&.to_f || 0) / 100) %></h2>
            <h2 class="last_br_rt">&nbsp;</h2>
            <h2 class="last_br_rt">&nbsp;</h2>
            <h2 class="<% if @other_coverages.blank? %>last_br_btm <% end %>last_br_rt">&nbsp;</h2>
            <% other_coverages.each.with_index do |cov, index| %>
            <h2 <% if index == other_coverages.length - 1 %>class="last_br_btm"<% end %>><%= cov.deductible ? ActionController::Base.helpers.number_to_currency(cov.deductible.to_f / 100) : raw("&nbsp;") %></h2>
            <% end %> 
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="remarks_head">
          <h2>REMARKS(Including SpecialConditions)</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="premium_in">
          <table cellpadding="5" cellspacing="0" style="border: none;">
            <tr>
              <td><h4>Premium:</h4></td>
              <td><h4><%= ActionController::Base.helpers.number_to_currency((@policy.premium.total_premium + @policy.premium.total_tax + @policy.premium.total_hidden_fee).to_f / 100) %></h4></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><h4>Admin Fees:</h4></td>
              <td><h4><%= ActionController::Base.helpers.number_to_currency((@policy.premium.total_fee - @policy.premium.total_hidden_fee).to_f / 100) %></h4></td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td><h2>Total:</h2></td>
              <td><h2><%= ActionController::Base.helpers.number_to_currency(@policy.premium.total.to_f / 100) %></h2></td>
            </tr>
          </table>
        </div>
        <div class="cancel_head">
          <h2>CANCELLATION</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="cancel_in">
          <h2>SHOULD ANY OF THE ABOVE DESCRIBED POLICIES BE CANCELLED BEFORE THE EXPIRATION DATE THEREOF, NOTICE WILL BE DELIVERED IN ACCORDANCE WITH THE POLICY PROVISIONS.</h2>
        </div>
      <% if @policy.primary_insurable.account %>
        <div class="cancel_head">
          <h2>ADDITIONAL INTEREST</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="add_main_blk clearfix">
          <div class="name_left flt_lt">
            <h4>NAME AND ADDRESS</h4>
            <h2><%= @policy.primary_insurable.account.title %></h2>
            <address><% if @policy.primary_insurable.account.primary_address; addr = @policy.primary_insurable.account.primary_address %>
              <%= addr.combined_street_address %> Apt. <%= addr.street_two %><br>
              <%= addr.city %>, <%= addr.state %>, <%= addr.combined_zip_code() %>
            <% end %></address>
          </div>
          <div class="sign_blk flt_lt clearfix">
            <div class="close flt_lt">
              <h2>X</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="pm_in flt_lt">
              <h3>PM</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="emp1 flt_lt">
              &nbsp;
            </div>
            <div class="emp2 flt_lt">
              &nbsp;
            </div>
            <div class="clearfix"></div>
            <div class="last_loan">
              <h4>LOAN #</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="auth">
              <h4>AUTHORIZED REPRESENTATIVE</h4>
              <figure>
                <img alt="ryan" height="35" src="https://gc-public-prod.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/assets/ryan-signature.png" width="136">
              </figure>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% elsif !@policy_application.extra_settings&.[]('additional_interest').blank? %>
      <% pm_info = @policy_application.extra_settings&.[]('additional_interest') %>
        <div class="cancel_head">
          <h2>ADDITIONAL INTEREST</h2>
        </div>
        <div class="add_main_blk clearfix">
          <div class="name_left flt_lt">
            <h4>NAME AND ADDRESS</h4>
            <h2><%= pm_info['entity_type'] == 'company' ? pm_info['company_name'] : [pm_info['first_name'], pm_info['middle_name'], pm_info['last_name']].select{|v| !v.blank? }.join(" ") %></h2>
            <address>
              <%= pm_info['addr1'] %><%= pm_info['addr2'].blank? ? '' : ", #{pm_info['addr2']}" %><br>
              <%= pm_info['city'] %>, <%= pm_info['state'] %> <%= pm_info['zip'] %>
            </address>
          </div>
          <div class="sign_blk flt_lt clearfix">
            <div class="close flt_lt">
              <h2>X</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="pm_in flt_lt">
              <h3>PM</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="emp1 flt_lt">
              &nbsp;
            </div>
            <div class="emp2 flt_lt">
              &nbsp;
            </div>
            <div class="clearfix"></div>
            <div class="last_loan">
              <h4>LOAN #</h4>
            </div>
            <div class="auth">
              <h4>AUTHORIZED REPRESENTATIVE</h4>
              <figure>
                <img alt="ryan" height="35" src="https://gc-public-prod.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/assets/ryan-signature.png" width="136">
              </figure>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
        <footer>
          <div class="acord_text">
            <p>ACORD27 (2001/12)</p>
          </div>
          <div class="copy_right">
            <p>Â© 1993-2009 ACORD CORPORATION. All rightsreserved.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="footer_cont">
            <p>The ACORD name and logo are registered marks of ACORD</p>
          </div>
        </footer>
      </div>
    </div><!-- wrapper ends -->
  </body>
</html>
